# Project Phases

## Phase 1: Setup & Architecture
**Goal**: Foundation and structure
**Duration**: ~2-3 weeks
**Deliverable**: Functional skeleton (Cargo project, basic Slint window, audio module stubs)
**Success**: Can compile, run, and see empty workbench UI

## Phase 2: Core Workbench
**Goal**: TTS integration and voice playback
**Duration**: ~3-4 weeks
**Deliverable**: Play/stop controls, waveform visualization, basic voice selection
**Success**: Can load TTS voice and play test audio

## Phase 3: Audio Processing
**Goal**: Equalizer, filters, synth integration
**Duration**: ~4-5 weeks
**Deliverable**: Working EQ, filter controls, basic synth voice options
**Success**: Can modify voice characteristics in real-time

## Phase 4: Modulation & Advanced
**Goal**: Voice modulation, analysis, preset system
**Duration**: ~3-4 weeks
**Deliverable**: Modulation effects, frequency analyzer, preset save/load
**Success**: Professional-grade voice manipulation capabilities

## Phase 5: Polish & Optimization
**Goal**: Performance, UX, documentation
**Duration**: ~2-3 weeks
**Deliverable**: Optimized code, complete docs, release-ready
**Success**: Production-ready application
